-story-about-solider-committing-suicide-after-arrest/00000190-bcdb-d3a7-a79e-fedbc9270000</guid></item><item><title>JD Vance 对以色列的立场如何？无论特朗普告诉他去哪里</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-16/ty-article/.highlight/where-will-j-d-vance-stand-on-israel-wherever-trump-tells-him-to/00000190-bca4-db2d-ab90-befef57a0000</link><description>任何参与其中的人都应该问自己：当万斯无人跟随时会发生什么？</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 18:25:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-16/ty-article/.highlight/where-will-j-d-vance-stand-on-israel-wherever-trump-tells-him-to/00000190-bca4-db2d-ab90-befef57a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队称其杀死了哈马斯一半的军事领导层，14,000名特工人员死伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/idf-killed-half-of-hamas-military-leadership-14-000-operatives-killed-or-wounded/00000190-bc9c-db47-abb0-befd45310000</link><description>以军认为，哈马斯陷入人力危机，对战地武装力量的指挥控制能力正在削弱，武装分子和指挥官的动机出现“裂痕”</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 17:55:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/idf-killed-half-of-hamas-military-leadership-14-000-operatives-killed-or-wounded/00000190-bc9c-db47-abb0-befd45310000</guid></item><item><title>以色列盟友警告称，西方国家将因财政部长斯莫特里奇在西岸的政策而对定居活动人士实施新制裁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/israels-allies-warn-of-new-western-sanctions-over-smotrichs-actions/00000190-bbd8-db47-abb0-bbf9bcc60000</link><description>被认为相对亲以色列的大卫·拉米本周作为英国外交大臣首次访问以色列，他在与以色列领导人的所有会晤中都提出了这个问题</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 17:29:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/israels-allies-warn-of-new-western-sanctions-over-smotrichs-actions/00000190-bbd8-db47-abb0-bbf9bcc60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 284 天：以色列军队称其杀死了哈马斯一半的军事领导层</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/isr